LOL Today I did a support troll pick. Only because I felt they deserved it. Dynamic Que I pick  {{champion:223}}  the ADC is first to ban and bans Tahm. This has happened 4 times now. I pick Tahm and MY team bans him because they don't pay attention to their team.  So thats what happened in this case I aske why? They said they didn't realize. So I pick my champion it was {{champion:98}}. I have supported as him and it can work. But I didn't go support. I went damage and I took kills and I carried the team in team fights. I do plan on doing this again if this situation does come up again. I mean it gives you like a 15 min timer to first pick your champion to show who you are playing. If my team somehow absolutely cannot pay attention to their team. Then I will be the hero who teaches them why they should pay attention. 

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 



But yeah trolling for no right reason is lame.

